---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="Laws of Life"
    description="The Laws of Life essay competition promotes character development and values-based learning for Green Local Schools students."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "Laws of Life", href: "/laws-of-life" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Building Character Through Writing</h2>
        <p>
            The Laws of Life essay competition is a powerful character development program that encourages students to identify and articulate the values and principles that guide their lives. Through reflective writing, students explore what matters most to them and how these "laws" shape their decisions and actions.
        </p>
        <p>
            This program helps students develop critical thinking skills, improve their writing abilities, and gain deeper self-awareness while reinforcing positive values that will serve them throughout their lives.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">2024-2025 Competition</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Important Dates</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Launch:</strong> October 1st</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Submission Deadline:</strong> February 28th</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Awards Ceremony:</strong> At Celebration of Education</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Participation Details</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Eligible:</strong> All Green Local Schools students</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Length:</strong> 500-800 words</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2V6h10a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm2 6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zm6 4a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Awards:</strong> Cash prizes and recognition</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>What is a "Law of Life"?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            A "Law of Life" is a principle, belief, or value that guides how you live your life. It might be something you learned from family, discovered through experience, or developed through reflection. These laws help us make decisions, overcome challenges, and interact with others.
        </p>

        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Examples of Laws of Life:</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>"Treat others the way you want to be treated"</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>"Hard work leads to success"</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>"Family comes first"</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>"Never give up on your dreams"</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>"Actions speak louder than words"</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your Essay Should Include:</h3>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="text-accent-600 text-xs font-semibold">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Your Law of Life</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Clearly state the principle or value you've chosen</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="text-accent-600 text-xs font-semibold">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Personal Story</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Share an experience that taught you this law</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="text-accent-600 text-xs font-semibold">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">How It Guides You</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Explain how this law influences your decisions</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="text-accent-600 text-xs font-semibold">4</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Future Impact</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Discuss how it will shape your future</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Award Categories</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Elementary School</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Grades K-5</p>
                <div class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">$100 Prize</div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Middle School</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Grades 6-8</p>
                <div class="text-accent-600 font-semibold">$150 Prize</div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">High School</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Grades 9-12</p>
                <div class="text-secondary-600 font-semibold">$200 Prize</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Writing Tips</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Getting Started</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li>• Think about values that are important to you</li>
                    <li>• Consider lessons you've learned from family or friends</li>
                    <li>• Reflect on challenges you've overcome</li>
                    <li>• Ask yourself: "What guides my decisions?"</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Writing Your Essay</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li>• Start with a compelling story or example</li>
                    <li>• Use specific details and personal experiences</li>
                    <li>• Show, don't just tell</li>
                    <li>• Connect your story to the broader principle</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Making It Memorable</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li>• Use vivid, descriptive language</li>
                    <li>• Include dialogue when appropriate</li>
                    <li>• Express genuine emotion and reflection</li>
                    <li>• End with a strong conclusion</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Final Review</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li>• Check spelling and grammar</li>
                    <li>• Read your essay aloud</li>
                    <li>• Ask a trusted adult to review it</li>
                    <li>• Make sure it stays within the word limit</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Past Winners</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Each year, we are inspired by the thoughtful essays submitted by Green Local Schools students. Here are some examples of Laws of Life that have been shared by past winners:
        </p>

        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4">
                <div class="text-primary-600 font-semibold mb-2">"Kindness is Contagious"</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Sarah, Grade 10</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                    "A simple act of kindness changed my perspective and taught me that small gestures can have big impacts."
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4">
                <div class="text-accent-600 font-semibold mb-2">"Failure is a Teacher"</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Marcus, Grade 8</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                    "My biggest mistake taught me the most important lesson about perseverance and learning from setbacks."
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4">
                <div class="text-secondary-600 font-semibold mb-2">"Honesty Builds Trust"</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Emma, Grade 5</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                    "When I told the truth even when it was hard, I learned that honesty makes relationships stronger."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Why Participate?</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Personal Growth</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    <li>• Develop self-awareness and reflection skills</li>
                    <li>• Strengthen your personal values</li>
                    <li>• Improve critical thinking abilities</li>
                    <li>• Build confidence in expressing your ideas</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Academic Benefits</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    <li>• Enhance writing and communication skills</li>
                    <li>• Practice essay structure and organization</li>
                    <li>• Receive recognition for your work</li>
                    <li>• Win cash prizes and certificates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Ready to Share Your Law of Life?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Students, teachers, and parents can get more information about the Laws of Life essay competition by contacting us.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Laws of Life Essay Competition" class="button-primary mr-4">
            Get More Information
        </a>
        <a href="/celebration-of-education" class="button-secondary">
            See Past Winners Celebrated
        </a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
